overview: Triple D Productions returns with the sequel Dna Bloodline 2. After being convicted of involuntary manslaughter, of Jazzmon King, Fly Dana Killebrew finally accepts the fact that it's time to change the way he moves. As Fly examines what in his Bloodline, he realizes that the very things that creates you can ultimately be the same things that destroys you.
title: DNA 2: Bloodline
